      const actions = [
        "💥 **Mad Max: Fury Road (2015)** - NON-STOP INSANITY! Charlize Theron kicks absolute butt, and the practical effects will blow your mind! Pure adrenaline rush!",
        "🔫 **John Wick (2014)** - Keanu Reeves + incredible choreography = PERFECTION! The action scenes are like deadly ballet, absolutely mesmerizing!",
        "🚗 **Mission: Impossible - Fallout (2018)** - Tom Cruise literally risked his life for these stunts! The helicopter chase will have you on the edge of your seat!",
        "🥊 **The Raid (2011)** - Indonesian martial arts masterpiece! The fight choreography is absolutely BRUTAL and beautiful at the same time!",
